      <title>[LO 3.3]</title>
      <list id="id1172364239926" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Fortunately, through careful excavations, <emphasis effect="bold">archaeologists</emphasis> have found quite a number of sources in caves and other places where these people probably lived earlier on.<figure id="id7868559"><media id="id7868559_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 1-3cb6.png" id="id7868559__onlineimage" height="143" width="151"/></media></figure><figure id="id7290259"><media id="id7290259_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 4-c2e3.png" id="id7290259__onlineimage" height="163" width="152"/></media></figure><figure id="id1172366350845"><media id="id1172366350845_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/Picture 7-4e59.png" id="id1172366350845__onlineimage" height="283" width="433"/></media></figure></item>
      </list>
      <list id="id4954415" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha" mark-suffix=")">
